/-- D6: `endpointReplyRecv` preserves `donationBudgetTransfer` (the reply leg unblocks the
target `.ready` + reschedules — `sameSchedContextBindings`; the receive leg is
`endpointReceiveDual`, which preserves the conjunct). -/
